OL,3,CAlmost 180,000 households to share
OL,4,C#18m in support payments
OL,6,FPensioners in Northern Ireland
OL,7,Faffected by cuts to winter fuel
OL,8,Fsupport are to receive a one-off
OL,9,Fpayment from Stormont in the coming
OL,10,Fweeks, a committee has heard.
OL,12,FPayments of #100 will be made to a
OL,13,Fsingle pensioner living alone, while a
OL,14,Fpayment of #50 will be made to each
OL,15,Feligible pensioner of a household if
OL,16,Fthere is more than one in the
OL,17,Fhousehold.
