OL,3,CAlmost 180,000 households to share
OL,4,C#18m in support payments
OL,6,FOfficials from the Department for
OL,7,FCommunities said they believe they are
OL,8,Fon track on deliver the payments
OL,9,Fbefore the end of March.
OL,11,FAn estimated 249,000 pensioners in the
OL,12,Fregion lost the winter fuel support
OL,13,Fpayment following a decision by the
OL,14,FLabour government last year to
OL,15,Frestrict it to only pensioners on
OL,16,Fcertain benefits.
