OL,3,CAlmost 180,000 households to share
OL,4,C#18m in support payments
OL,6,FStormont Communities Minister Gordon
OL,7,FLyons announced last November a one-
OL,8,Foff payment for those affected by the
OL,9,Fcut, and secured #17million from an in-
OL,10,Fyear monitoring fund for the move.
OL,12,FThe Pension Age Fuel Support Payment
OL,13,FScheme is aimed to be delivered before
OL,14,Fthe end of March, with payments to be
OL,15,Fdelivered directly into bank accounts.
