OL,3,CAlmost 180,000 households to share
OL,4,C#18m in support payments
OL,6,FAppearing at the Stormont Communities
OL,7,FCommittee on Thursday morning, David
OL,8,FTarr said the total value of the
OL,9,Fpayments is estimated to be around
OL,10,F#18m, excluding administration and IT
OL,11,Fcosts.
OL,13,FConrad McConnell said following the
OL,14,Fannouncement by the minister that work
OL,15,Fstarted "immediately" to get the
OL,16,Fpayment out.
OL,18,F"There are an estimated 179,000
OL,19,Fhouseholds in Northern Ireland
OL,20,Fexpected to receive this payment," he
OL,21,Fsaid.
