OL,3,CAlmost 180,000 households to share
OL,4,C#18m in support payments
OL,6,F"We started worked immediately once
OL,7,Fthe announcement was made to put in
OL,8,Fall the necessary IT and logistical
OL,9,Farrangements to ensure the issuing of
OL,10,Fthe payments before the end of March.
OL,12,F"We have a dedicated team in place
OL,13,Fwhich meets weekly and works on this
OL,14,Fevery day to make this happen on time.
OL,15,FThere are lots of strands involved in
OL,16,Fthis work.
OL,18,F"But despite all the complexity across
OL,19,Fall the various strands of work ... we
OL,20,Fare on track to have the payment paid
OL,21,Fbefore the end of March 2025."
